<p rend="chapter">Vatthuvisodhanīgāthā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="4"><hi rend="paranum">4</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Buddhoti ko buddhaguṇo ti ko so,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Acintayādittamupāgato yo;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Anaññasādhāraṇabhūtamatthaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Akāsi kiṃ so kimavoca buddho.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="5"><hi rend="paranum">5</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Visuddhakhandhasantāno buddhoti niyamo kato,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Khandhasantānasuddhī tu guṇoti niyamo kato.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="6"><hi rend="paranum">6</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Akāsi kiccāni dinesu pañca,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Pasādayañciddhibalena sena;</p>

<p rend="gatha3">Janānasesaṃ cariyānukūlaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Ñatvānavocānusayappahānaṃ.</p>
